Part Hugo How to create a Hugo website This is a good tutorial.
However, the themes may contain bugs. (The best way is to download another theme!)
 Language Code Error:  Some theme use site.LanguageCode and others use site.Lang.LanguageCode   Code Highlight Error:  Change it to .post-content pre code { word-break: normal !important; white-space: pre !important; }
